window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>In this audio-first rom com by #1 New York Times bestselling author Lauren Blakely, a scorching one-night stand with a stranger turns into a deliciously forbidden romance... </b></p> <p>My first evening in London feels like kismet when I bump into a charming, book-loving Englishman, and by the end of the night, he’s making me see stars. I’m floating when we make plans to meet again.</p> <p>Then fate decides to pull a fast one on me.</p> <p>Turns out, my smoldering new lover is my red-hot competition, and we’re vying for the same promotion at the elite auction house I crossed an ocean for.</p> <p>If that’s not enough, the hottie and I are forced to work together on a brand new collection. Every. Single. Tempting. Day.</p> <p>What's an American woman in London to do?</p> <p>Staying far, far away would be the safe choice, especially when I learn about his past and how it mirrors mine. But I don’t always play it safe with my heart… </p>"; 
